Some of optimization algorithms previously utilized to tackle the pressure vessel design problem include OBLGOA, RW-GWO, OBSCA, MHDA, WOA, HHO and FCGHMD. The performance of the CCHHO algorithm on optimizing this design problem is compared with that of these algorithms and CCNMHHO. The comparison outcomes in Table 6 report the optimal cost of 5826.47696325. It reveals meaningfully that the CCHHO is the most effective optimizer among above well-established ones in this engineering design case.Table 6
